text_tabs.value: The outdoor amenities of this property are just as impressive, with a 545+/- square foot shop that offers additional space for hobbies or storage, while the backyard swimming pool, complete with a deck, provides the perfect spot for summer fun and relaxation. One of the highlights of this property is its stunning lakefront view on Indian Lake, offering a peaceful and scenic backdrop to everyday life. Whether you enjoy fishing, kayaking, or simply relaxing by the water, this home delivers a lifestyle of leisure and natural beauty
